{"tid":1727632,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急資訊！有嘢想問下大家","createTime":"2019-11-16T13:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T21:51:45.000Z","uid":184307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1c8b9de8d21df6c57cb324c5a9cc7c950de8da5f","tid":1727632,"uid":184307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:35:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99a67a26929c949527d1a8db1e4561220da573b","tid":1727632,"uid":229923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:37:11.000Z","msg":"冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4cbece666fb3d8bba38b358dc8624c1dd5853f9","tid":1727632,"uid":68084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:38:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Facebook: Kevin Hui<br />\n<br />\n中文名:許家偉<br />\n<br />\n中學:香港中文大學校友會聯會陳震夏中學<br />\n<br />\n大專:HKCC</span></span><br />\n<br />\n事源就係女朋友係facebook無啦啦有個三唔識七既人inobx佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kx8wuNP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKx8wuNP.png&h=507fbd36&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n仲要問一唔一齊出去,真係唔知咩心態<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係facebook PO下新聞扮同路人<br />\n<br />\n實際上就係想借呢件事黎食女<br />\n<br />\n絲打真係要小心<br />\n<br />\n狗公ig:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7NWNMVs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7NWNMVs.jpg&h=58c06442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條撚樣仲要好似有女朋友?<br />\n做佢女朋友真係慘<br />\n<br />\n絲打們認住呢條撚樣,踢波既 小心佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gc2k6Wh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgc2k6Wh.png&h=893df396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n垃圾狗公咁撚鍾意消費呢場運動?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r30ZC4p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr30ZC4p.png&h=bda94586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n返去玩玩具啦屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">絲打們要小心,好撚多呢種垃圾狗公借機搵食<br />\n<br />\n特別係呢條死狗公 許家偉!!</span>"},{"pid":"764b5692a8b2eef87c4bab8881a02e059c939d8d","tid":1727632,"uid":184307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b99a67a26929c949527d1a8db1e4561220da573b","tid":1727632,"uid":229923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:37:11.000Z","msg":"冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:38:22.000Z","msg":"認真問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51113804e2ad04d6ab2981ca31b2879e11c69763","tid":1727632,"uid":229923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b99a67a26929c949527d1a8db1e4561220da573b","tid":1727632,"uid":229923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:37:11.000Z","msg":"冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:38:54.000Z","msg":"不如你去睇下k kwong既fd page睇下啲資訊，可能幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />保重"},{"pid":"1ab0befaf8aaffce90601456798eaa44590a160e","tid":1727632,"uid":229923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51113804e2ad04d6ab2981ca31b2879e11c69763","tid":1727632,"uid":229923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b99a67a26929c949527d1a8db1e4561220da573b","tid":1727632,"uid":229923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:37:11.000Z","msg":"冇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:38:54.000Z","msg":"不如你去睇下k kwong既fd page睇下啲資訊，可能幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />保重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:39:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">facebook</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7feab6f390971703195e017973e23e78f0f01988","tid":1727632,"uid":184307,"like"